    "title": "Principal Frontend Developer at Zoho Corporation Holdings Services",
    "description": "Zoho Corporation Holdings Services is actively seeking a talented and motivated Frontend Developer to join our dynamic team in Chandigarh. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Zoho Corporation Holdings Services:\nZoho Corporation Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in AWS\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Chandigarh, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zoho Corporation Holdings Services!",
